			<subsection name="To verify Bigtop releases using GPG:" id="gpg"></subsection>
			<ol>
				<li>
					Download the release bigtop-X.Y.Z-project.tar.gz from links above.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					Download the signature file pgp(bigtop-X.Y.Z-project.tar.gz.asc) from links above.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					Download the <a href="https://apache.org/dist/bigtop/KEYS">Bigtop KEYS</a> file.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					$ gpg --import KEYS<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					$ gpg --verify bigtop-X.Y.Z-src.tar.gz.asc<br/>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<subsection name="To verify Bigtop releases using SHA-256 or SHA-512:" id="checksum"></subsection>
			<ol>
				<li>
					Download the release bigtop-X.Y.Z-project.tar.gz from links above.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					Download the checksum file sha256/512 from links above.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					$ shasum -a 256 bigtop-X.Y.Z-src.tar.gz<br/>
					$ shasum -a 512 bigtop-X.Y.Z-src.tar.gz<br/>
				</li>
			</ol>
			<subsection name="To verify Bigtop releases using SHA-1 or MD5(previous releases only):" id="checksum_prev"></subsection>
			<ol>
				<li>
					Download the release bigtop-X.Y.Z-project.tar.gz from links above.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					Download the checksum file sha1 or md5 from links above.<br/>
				</li>
				<li>
					$ shasum bigtop-X.Y.Z-src.tar.gz<br/>
					$ md5 bigtop-X.Y.Z-src.tar.gz<br/>
				</li>
